{
  "stem": "7904.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have-- you have the Ukrainian, you had the Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, the eastern part of Poland-- eastern part of Europe was very, very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see my nose?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My nose was-- got crooked because young Poles throw a big, big stone and they hit my nose and fall.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was in 19-- I think this was-- that happened in 1938.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by my head was swollen for weeks and weeks till later on I didn't want to do anything [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the nose remained till today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I also felt very, very big-- very great anti-Semitism in the schools.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They always beat up the Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They always beat up the Jews-- the young Poles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After the war, when I came back to my hometown to find out if somebody is still alive, they-- the only-- the only question from the Poles was, you're still alive?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You're still alive?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So many Jews came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So many Jews came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I asked them, how many Jews?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Six?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Eight?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They still had-- in their mind, they still had the hate, till today.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Till today they hate the Jews most-- I-- most than anybody else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we felt-- sure, we felt-- for instance, in the wintertime, they used to throw snowballs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put in piece of a-- piece of a [NON-ENGLISH]-- a piece of, let's say, coals or to-- for the balls, for the snowballs to be harder, and we should feel it more than otherwise.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] Also, about three, four years before the war, a priest went into the same business what my father was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came in with a lot of money and so and so, with-- and he wanted to be a competition.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
